dashboard_elements.body_text:
Help Resources: Office Hours | Intro Training Webinar | Viva Engage Analytics Community | Web Analytics Guide & Glossary
Site (Disabled, Do Not Use): This filter has been disabled, so the 3 individual website results can load correctly. Please disregard this filter box.
URL, Title, Section, Sub Section: These filters apply to the relevant website only. For example, if you filter URL by https://www.workbc.ca/, only the WorkBC results will appear. The other two sites' results will be blank.
URL, Title, Section, Sub Section: These filters are disabled for the Career Transition Tool section, WorkBC Assorted Report, WorkBC CT & CTT Custom Report and Career Search Tool Custom Report section - Users, Page Views and Sessions tiles.
